g 661w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 661px) 100vw, 661px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 테스트 프레임워크를 선택합니다. 선택할 수 있는 테스트 프레임워크는 여러개가 존재하지만 저는 “junit jufiter”를 선택하겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 577px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.777777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAhUlEQVQI111OwQrFIAzT60BkTufcEFF0HsT//7w8Wthg7xCSpm1a4ZzDdV04zxMhBFBN2nvPNel933mGesdxQCkFIQSklJBSsH5hjOHl3jtSSrjvG7VWRinlZQpfloVDPgH/yDnzQmuNec6JGCN/Yq1l7zk0xmD/+Zbm6JDWGuu6Yts2/ADBX0qj8yyrxgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"insert_project_name\"\n        title=\"insert_project_name\"\n        src=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/gradle_start_project-init-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/e9ff0/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 180w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/f21e7/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 360w,\n/static/9eec2dbffa1857ec427ccbf7f542587e/065e2/gradle_start_project-init-5.png 577w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 프로젝트 명을 입력합니다. 디폴트 값은 폴더의 이름을 따라가지만 다른 프로젝트 명을 입력할 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p>설정을 전부 끝마쳤다면 설정한 옵션에 맞춰 Gradle 프로젝트가 생성됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\">환경</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gralde-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gralde 프로젝트 시작하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#gradle-install-hombrew\">Gradle Install Hombrew</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">1. 프로젝트 시작 폴더 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-gradle-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">2. Gradle 프로젝트 생성</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 28, 2022","title":"[Gradle] Gradle project 시작하기","categories":"Java","author":"chanjin_ahn","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/Java/start_gradle_project/gradle_start_project/"}},"prev":{"id":"cd245c56-b4f5-5b1e-a951-8ddba072ab7a","html":"<h2 id=\"환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>환경</h2>\n<hr>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">종류</th>\n<th>환경</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OS</td>\n<td>M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IDE</td>\n<td>Intellij(2022.1.2)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"gradle-project-에-lombok-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gradle project 에 lombok 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Project 에 Lombok 적용하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>주로 라이브러리에 추가하는 통상적인 방법과 달리 Gralde Project는 라이브러리를 추가하지 않아도 plugin 으로 간단히 Lombok을 적용할 수 있습니다.\n<a href=\"https://plugins.gradle.org/plugin/io.freefair.lombok\">lombok plugins guide</a> 에 접속하여 버전과 적용 방법을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bulidgradle-에-lombok-plugin-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bulidgradle-%EC%97%90-lombok-plugin-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"bulidgradle 에 lombok plugin 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bulid.gradle 에 lombok plugin 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    plugins <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id \"io.freefair.lombok\" version \"6.5.0.2\"\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>라이브러리 추가 뿐만 아니라 annotation 설정을 해야하는 일반 gradle 환경과 달리 간단하게 적용할 수 있는 것이 가장 큰 장점입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"intellij-에-lombok-설정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"intellij 에 lombok 설정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ 에 Lombok 설정하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"플러그인-목록에-lombok-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"플러그인 목록에 lombok 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플러그인 목록에 Lombok 추가</h3>\n<p>최신 Intellij 는 기본 플러그인에 Lombok 이 포함되어 있으며 플러그인 활성화가 되어있습니다. 따라서 정상적으로 활성화 되어있는지 확인만 하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">Setting > Plugins</code> 를 차례로 클릭한 뒤 상단의 <code class=\"language-text\">Installed</code> 탭을 클릭합니다. 그 후 검색창에 <strong>Lombok</strong> 이 깔려있는지, 체크박스가 체크되어있는지 확인하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"lombok-download_plugin.png\" alt=\"lombok plugin download\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"intellij-설정-중-annotaion-processing-을-활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91-annotaion-processing-%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"intellij 설정 중 annotaion processing 을 활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ 설정 중 Annotaion Processing 을 활성화</h3>\n<p>마지막으로 Annotation Processing 이 활성화 되어있는지 확인합니다.</p>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">Setting > Build, Execution, Deployment > Compiler > Annotation Processors</code> 를 차례로 클릭한 뒤 <code class=\"language-text\">Enable annotation processing</code> 이 체크 되어있는지 확인하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png\" alt=\"annotation processing enable\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"적용-테스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"적용 테스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용 테스트</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>위 내용을 그대로 따랐을 경우 설정이 모두 끝났습니다. lombok annotation 을 사용하여 제대로 적용하였는지 확인합니다.\n예제에서는 @Sl4j annotation 을 사용하여 제대로 설정하였는지 테스트 하도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">lombok<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>extern<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>slf4j<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Slf4j</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Slf4j</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LombokAnnotationTest</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> args<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        log<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lombok 의 {} annotation 을 사용하여 적용되었는지 테스트합니다. \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@Sl4j\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"lombok-result.png\" alt=\"test result\"></p>\n<p>이상으로 Gradle Project 에 Lombok 을 간단히 적용하는 방법에 대해서 알아보았습니다. 감사합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\">환경</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gradle Project 에 Lombok 적용하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#bulidgradle-%EC%97%90-lombok-plugin-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">bulid.gradle 에 lombok plugin 추가</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">IntelliJ 에 Lombok 설정하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">플러그인 목록에 Lombok 추가</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91-annotaion-processing-%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\">IntelliJ 설정 중 Annotaion Processing 을 활성화</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\">적용 테스트</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"June 20, 2022","title":"[Java] gradle project lombok 설정","categories":"Java Spring","author":"chanjin_ahn","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/Java/start_gradle_project/lombok/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://chanjinahn.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"ChanjinAhn/ChanjinAhn.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Java/Path/","nextSlug":"/Java/start_gradle_project/gradle_start_project/","prevSlug":"/Java/start_gradle_project/lombok/"}},
